{
  "texts": [
    "We had hoped to build a digital agent with the goal of consistently surveilling the medical literature, identifying relevant articles of interest to a given specialty, and forwarding them to a user.",
    "Chat-GPT's inability to reliably classify the relevance of specific articles limits our ability to construct such an agent.",
    "We hope that in future iterations of LLMs, these tools will become more capable of relevance classification.",
    "We are not aware of prior studies that have systematically evaluated GPT-3.5's ability to summarize medical abstracts with a focus on quality, accuracy, and bias.",
    "However, our data are concordant with prior evidence suggesting reasonable performance for summarization in other domains (eg, news)."
  ]
}